title: The title of hyperlink builder should be 'Hyperlink Options', now it changes with settings.
OB: When clicking on 'OK' and then reopening the hyperlink builder, the actual result is that its title becomes 'www.actuate.com'.
EB: The expected result is that the hyperlink builder title should be 'Hyperlink Options'.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:
1. Click on 'OK' in the hyperlink builder.
2. Reopen the hyperlink builder & observe the changed title.
